arStrings.szText: Oh, just reading this fellow's entrails.
The goatmen are encroaching ever more on our lands. I'm trying to determine why, how.
With a bit of skill, you can learn a lot from someone's innards. Not many remember or practice the old ways, but you split the gut and read the mess that pours out...
Help me open the gut further, will you? I'm not getting a good reading, and my hands aren't as steady as they used to be.
